{"tid":1850290,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"社會主義特色 - 在四川廣漢，一戶人家的女婿從武漢回去","createTime":"2020-01-29T12:45:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T12:52:12.000Z","uid":278117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ca8163b2d811318e557badd0fe0c9f8237cd8b32","tid":1850290,"uid":278117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T12:45:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RFAChinese/videos/2758877700848548/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRFAChinese%2Fvideos%2F2758877700848548%2F&d=m5XrLHEHhhS4xH%2BSicsBH34WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=2a04c277\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RFAChinese/videos/2758877700848548/</a><br />\n<br />\n在四川廣漢，一戶人家的女婿從武漢回去，但這家人一直隱瞞，並每天到處打牌，最後發病。鄰居憤怒地到這戶人家聲討，眾人包圍在門外怒罵，更有居民用長棍怒砸家門，公安嘗試阻止都不成功。"},{"pid":"3a6d2ddf78f0208020b854c533a50da790ef1787","tid":1850290,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T12:52:12.000Z","msg":"入唔到屋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}